com.novartis.opensource.yada

Class JSONParamsEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.novartis.opensource.yada.JSONParamsEntry

  • public class JSONParamsEntry
extends Object
    An internally used data structure encapsulating data and params associated to a YADAQuery via qname, passed to the framework in a request.
    Since:
    0.4.0.0
    Author:
    David Varon
    See Also:
    JSONParams
